            <h2 class="resources-heading">How We Help</h2>
            <div class="g g-4up">

               <div class="gi resource-block">
                                    <a href="/seminars/">
                     <img src="http://smallbusinessbc.ca/wp-content/themes/sbbcmain/images/circle-icons/icon-education.svg" onerror="this.src='http://smallbusinessbc.ca/wp-content/themes/sbbcmain/images/circle-icons/icon-education.png'" alt="Education" />
                  </a>
                  <h3><a href="/seminars/">Business Education</a></h3>
                  <p>Business theory is one thing. Applying it is another. We teach practical skills and knowledge you can use in the real world.</p>                  <span class="service-cta">
                     <a href="/seminars/">Find out more &#9654;</a>
                  </span>
               </div>

               <div class="gi resource-block">
                                    <a href="/services/ask-the-expert/">
                     <img src="http://smallbusinessbc.ca/wp-content/themes/sbbcmain/images/circle-icons/icon-advice.svg" onerror="this.src='http://smallbusinessbc.ca/wp-content/themes/sbbcmain/images/circle-icons/icon-advice.png'" alt="Expert Advice" />
                  </a>
                  <h3><a href="/services/ask-the-expert/">Expert Advice &amp; Help</a></h3>
                  <p>Bouncing ideas off of friends and family can be helpful, but it's no substitute for talking to a qualified expert.</p>                  <span class="service-cta">
                     <a href="/services/ask-the-expert/">Find out more &#9654;</a>
                  </span>
               </div>

